'''无聊公司'''（{{lang-en|The Boring Company}}）<ref>{{Citation|journal=Department of State|publisher=State of Delaware|last=Division of Corporations|title=TBC – The Boring Company|id=6279803|date=2017-01-11}}</ref><ref name="Chafkin">{{Cite web|title=Elon Musk Is Really Boring|url=https://www.bloomberg.com/news/features/2017-02-16/elon-musk-is-really-boring|accessdate=2017-02-16|author=Chafkin|date=2017-02-16|first=Max|publisher=Bloomberg|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20170216113314/https://www.bloomberg.com/news/features/2017-02-16/elon-musk-is-really-boring|archivedate=2017-02-16}}</ref>，“Boring”語帶雙關，既有“无聊的”又有“钻孔”的意思，是由[[伊隆·马斯克|伊隆·马斯克]]创立的美国基础设施和隧道建设公司。尽管其目前的项目是为城市内部交通系统而设计，但该公司表示，[[霍桑_(加利福尼亚州)|霍桑]]的试验隧道可以用于[[超迴路列車|超级高铁]]研发，而目前在建的隧道也支持最终过渡到城际超级高铁。<ref name="projects2020">{{Cite news|url=https://www.boringcompany.com/projects/|title=The Boring Company Projects page: 2020|publisher=The Boring Company|date=2020-11-11|accessdate=2020-11-11|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20201111175424/https://www.boringcompany.com/projects/|archivedate=2020-11-11}}</ref><ref name="faq2020">{{Cite news|url=https://www.boringcompany.com/faq/|title=The Boring Company FAQ: 2020|publisher=The Boring Company|date=2020-11-12|accessdate=2020-11-12|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20201112053938/https://www.boringcompany.com/faq/|archivedate=2020-11-12}}</ref>

无聊公司已在洛杉矶县完成了一条用于测试超级高铁和以特斯拉電動車为载具的[[鑽洞試驗隧道|隧道]]，还正在拉斯维加斯建设另一条可以运行特斯拉電動車的隧道。另外还有两条隧道尚待批准，其中一条连接华盛顿特区和巴尔的摩，另一条会把[[道奇體育場|道奇体育场]]与洛杉矶其余地区连接起来。<ref name="projects2020">{{Cite news|url=https://www.boringcompany.com/projects/|title=The Boring Company Projects page: 2020|publisher=The Boring Company|date=2020-11-11|accessdate=2020-11-11|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20201111175424/https://www.boringcompany.com/projects/|archivedate=2020-11-11}}</ref>

马斯克表示成立无聊公司的动机是洛杉矶交通问题以及当前二维运输网络的局限性。<ref name="Chafkin">{{Cite web|title=Elon Musk Is Really Boring|url=https://www.bloomberg.com/news/features/2017-02-16/elon-musk-is-really-boring|accessdate=2017-02-16|author=Chafkin|date=2017-02-16|first=Max|publisher=Bloomberg|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20170216113314/https://www.bloomberg.com/news/features/2017-02-16/elon-musk-is-really-boring|archivedate=2017-02-16}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|title=Elon Musk on Digging Big-Ass Tunnel: 'We Have No Idea What We're Doing'|url=https://gizmodo.com/elon-musk-on-digging-big-ass-tunnel-we-have-no-idea-wh-1791803837|accessdate=2017-02-17|author=Peyser|date=2017-01-30|first=Eve|publisher=Gizmodo|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20170219045530/http://gizmodo.com/elon-musk-on-digging-big-ass-tunnel-we-have-no-idea-wh-1791803837|archivedate=2017-02-19}}</ref>无聊公司最初是SpaceX的[[子公司|子公司]]<ref name="hawthore20180911">[http://hawthorne-ca.granicus.com/MetaViewer.php?view_id=&event_id=490&meta_id=35783 Agenda Item No. 9, City of Hawthorne City Council, Agenda Bill] {{Wayback|url=http://hawthorne-ca.granicus.com/MetaViewer.php?view_id=&event_id=490&meta_id=35783 |date=20210224164217 }}, 11 September 2018, Planning & Community Development Department, City of Hawthorne. Retrieved 13 September 2018.</ref>，在2018年成为独立公司。<ref name="wsj20181217">{{Cite news|author=Copeland|first=Rob|url=https://www.wsj.com/articles/elon-musks-new-boring-co-faced-questions-over-spacex-financial-ties-11545078371|title=Elon Musk's New Boring Co. Faced Questions Over SpaceX Financial Ties|work=[[The_Wall_Street_Journal|The Wall Street Journal]]|date=2018-12-17|accessdate=2018-12-18|quote=''When the Boring Co. was earlier this year spun into its own firm, more than 90% of the equity went to Mr. Musk and the rest to early employees, ... The Boring Co. has since given some equity to SpaceX as compensation for the help, ... about 6% of Boring stock, “based on the value of land, time and other resources contributed since creation of the company,” ''|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20181218044810/https://www.wsj.com/articles/elon-musks-new-boring-co-faced-questions-over-spacex-financial-ties-11545078371|archivedate=2018-12-18}}</ref>截至2018年12月，马斯克拥有90％的[[股東權益|股份]]<ref>{{Cite web|title=Archived copy|url=https://www.theverge.com/2018/12/19/18148061/boring-tunnel-test-drive-hawthorne-tesla-elon-musk|accessdate=2018-12-20|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20181220231741/https://www.theverge.com/2018/12/19/18148061/boring-tunnel-test-drive-hawthorne-tesla-elon-musk|archivedate=2018-12-20}}</ref>，因为公司初创时期利用了SpaceX的资源，[[SpaceX|SpaceX]]拥有6％的股份。<ref>{{Cite web|title=Elon Musk's New Boring Co. Faced Questions Over SpaceX Financial Ties|url=https://www.wsj.com/articles/elon-musks-new-boring-co-faced-questions-over-spacex-financial-ties-11545078371|accessdate=2018-12-18|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20181218044810/https://www.wsj.com/articles/elon-musks-new-boring-co-faced-questions-over-spacex-financial-ties-11545078371|archivedate=2018-12-18}}</ref>2019年的外部投资改变了股权格局。

== 公司历史 ==
[[File:Elon_Musk_at_TED_2017.jpeg|缩略图]]
[[伊隆·马斯克|伊隆·马斯克]]在2016年12月对外提到无聊公司。<ref name="musk20161218">{{Cite web|title=Elon Musk's Next Venture to Tackle Traffic Is Totally 'Boring'|url=http://fortune.com/2016/12/18/elon-musk-traffic-boring/|accessdate=2017-02-17|author=Gajanan|date=2016-12-18|first=Mahita|work=Fortune|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20170216134820/http://fortune.com/2016/12/18/elon-musk-traffic-boring/|archivedate=2017-02-16}}</ref>2017年2月，该公司已开始在[[SpaceX|SpaceX]]位于[[霍桑_(加利福尼亚州)|霍索恩]]办公区挖掘30英尺（9米）宽，50英尺（15米）长，15英尺（4.6米）深的测试沟槽，因为在这个区域内施工无需任何[[獨立機關|许可]]。<ref name="Chafkin">{{Cite web|title=Elon Musk Is Really Boring|url=https://www.bloomberg.com/news/features/2017-02-16/elon-musk-is-really-boring|accessdate=2017-02-16|author=Chafkin|date=2017-02-16|first=Max|publisher=Bloomberg|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20170216113314/https://www.bloomberg.com/news/features/2017-02-16/elon-musk-is-really-boring|archivedate=2017-02-16}}</ref><ref name=":1">{{Cite web|title=Elon Musk's boring machine has already built a 'test trench' in Hawthorne, CA|url=https://www.wired.co.uk/article/elon-musk-tunnel-boring|accessdate=2017-02-19|author=Heathman|first=Amelia|language=en-Glenn Beck|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20170718214211/http://www.wired.co.uk/article/elon-musk-tunnel-boring|archivedate=2017-07-18}}</ref>一个星期五下午，当听到需要至少两周才能把员工的车从停车场挪走以开始挖掘之后，马斯克说：“今天就开始，全天24小时不间断地挖，看看到星期天下午能挖多大。”那天晚些时候，汽车就都不见了，地上则出现了一个洞。<ref name="rollingstone20171115">{{Cite news|author=Strauss|first=Neil|title=Elon Musk: The Architect of Tomorrow|url=https://www.rollingstone.com/culture/features/elon-musk-inventors-plans-for-outer-space-cars-finding-love-w511747|accessdate=2017-11-15|work=Rolling Stone|date=2017-11-15|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20171115134819/http://www.rollingstone.com/culture/features/elon-musk-inventors-plans-for-outer-space-cars-finding-love-w511747|archivedate=2017-11-15}}</ref> 

在2017年4月的[[TED大会|TED大会]]上的一次采访中，马斯克估计，无聊公司占用了他2％至3％的时间，是他的个人爱好。<ref>{{Cite web|title=The future we're building – and boring – Elon Musk|url=https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=zIwLWfaAg-8&t=10m29s|author=TED|date=2017-05-03|access-date=2021-01-09|archive-date=2021-08-23|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210823172825/https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=zIwLWfaAg-8&t=10m29s|dead-url=no}}</ref>

2017年3月，马斯克宣布，公司4月将开始使用[[隧道掘進機|隧道掘进机]]在SpaceX上挖掘实用的隧道。<ref>{{Cite web|title=Elon Musk: We Start Digging the Tunnel Under L.A. Next Month|url=https://futurism.com/elon-musk-we-start-digging-the-tunnel-under-l-a-next-month/|accessdate=2017-04-11|author=Galeon|date=2017-03-24|first=Dom|work=Futurism|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20170412142823/https://futurism.com/elon-musk-we-start-digging-the-tunnel-under-l-a-next-month/|archivedate=2017-04-12}}</ref>2017年4月底，在SpaceX出现了侧面印有无聊公司的掘进机。<ref>{{Cite web|title=We just got our first glimpse of Elon Musk's new tunnel company|url=http://www.businessinsider.com/elon-musk-launches-boring-company-to-dig-tunnels-2017-4|accessdate=2017-05-10|work=Business Insider|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20170515191545/http://www.businessinsider.com/elon-musk-launches-boring-company-to-dig-tunnels-2017-4|archivedate=2017-05-15}}</ref>这台机器的名称“戈多”于2017年5月公开，源自[[萨缪尔·贝克特|萨缪尔·贝克特]]的戏剧[[等待戈多|等待戈多]]。之后的掘进机也都以诗歌和戏剧来命名。<ref name=":0">{{Cite web|title=All the quirky details you need to know about Elon Musk's Boring company|url=https://money.cnn.com/2017/07/08/technology/future/elon-musk-boring-company/index.html|accessdate=2020-03-22|author=Wattles|date=2017-07-08|first=Jackie|work=CNNMoney|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20200322205737/https://money.cnn.com/2017/07/08/technology/future/elon-musk-boring-company/index.html|archivedate=2020-03-22}}</ref>马斯克表示第一条路线会从[[洛杉磯國際機場|洛杉矶国际机场]]开始，经[[卡尔弗城_(加利福尼亚州)|卡尔弗市]]，再到[[圣莫尼卡|圣莫尼卡]]，终点在[[西木區|西木区]]。他声称，地上行驶（从机场到西木区）需要45分钟，而使用隧道需要5分钟。<ref>{{Cite web|title=Elon Musk's new video of his underground tunnel project will make you nauseous|url=https://www.theverge.com/2017/5/12/15629754/elon-musk-boring-company-tunnels-watch-first-route-la|accessdate=2017-05-12|author=Hawkins|date=2017-05-12|first=Andrew J.|work=[[The_Verge|The Verge]]|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20170705122117/https://www.theverge.com/2017/5/12/15629754/elon-musk-boring-company-tunnels-watch-first-route-la|archivedate=2017-07-05}}</ref>按计划，汽车会被放在电动雪橇上，并以120英里每小时（200公里每小时）的速度通过隧道。2017年11月，无聊公司向[[洛杉矶|洛杉矶]]政府[[獨立機關|监管机构]]提出许可申请，要求修建一条从[[霍桑_(加利福尼亚州)|霍桑]]出发，沿[[405号州际公路_(加利福尼亚州)|405号州际公路]]通往西木区的隧道。<ref name="lat20171121">{{Cite web|title=Elon Musk's tunneling company wants to dig through L.A.|url=https://www.latimes.com/local/lanow/la-me-ln-elon-musk-boring-company-20171121-story.html|accessdate=2018-03-26|author=Nelson|first=Laura J.|work=Los Angeles Times|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20180327084136/http://www.latimes.com/local/lanow/la-me-ln-elon-musk-boring-company-20171121-story.html|archivedate=2018-03-27}}</ref>

与洛杉矶项目同时宣布的还有纽约到华盛顿特区地下运行的超级高铁（密封管）。<ref name="inverse20171215">{{Cite news|date=2017-12-15|title=When Boring Company Will Start Digging Northeast Hyperloop, Gov Docs Reveal : It's sooner than you think|work=[[Inverse_(website)|Inverse]]|url=https://www.inverse.com/article/39460-elon-musk-hyperloop-boring-company|accessdate=2018-01-11|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20180112042730/https://www.inverse.com/article/39460-elon-musk-hyperloop-boring-company|archivedate=2018-01-12}}</ref>马斯克声称从一个市中心到另一个市中心只需29分钟。 
其他可能的项目包括从一条[[旧金山|旧金山]]到洛杉矶，以及一条在[[德克萨斯州|德克萨斯州]]的超级高铁。<ref name="musk20170720">
{{Cite tweet|number=888059982586839041|user=elonmusk|title=For sure. First set of tunnels are to alleviate greater LA urban congestion. Will start NY–DC in parallel. Then prob LA-SF and a TX loop.|date=July 20, 2017|access-date=July 21, 2017|last=Musk|first=Elon}}</ref>

2017年7月，马斯克上传了一段视频，展示了汽车电梯原型的测试情况。<ref>{{Cite news|url=https://www.theverge.com/tldr/2017/7/26/16031262/elon-must-boring-tunnel-elevator|title=Elon Musk reveals Boring car elevator|work=The Verge|accessdate=2017-07-26|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20170726135645/https://www.theverge.com/tldr/2017/7/26/16031262/elon-must-boring-tunnel-elevator|archivedate=2017-07-26}}</ref> 10月，马斯克透露第二台隧道掘进机名为“线风暴”，以[[羅伯特·佛洛斯特|罗伯特·弗罗斯特]]的诗作《线风暴之歌》命名。<ref>{{Cite web|title=The Boring Company will add second tunneling machine "Line-storm" to its fleet|url=https://www.teslarati.com/the-boring-company-line-storm-second-tunneling-machine/|accessdate=2017-10-27|work=teslarati.com|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20171027231845/https://www.teslarati.com/the-boring-company-line-storm-second-tunneling-machine/|archivedate=2017-10-27}}</ref>
